+        "- Evidently HTML and JSON artifacts for data drift\n",
+        "- Evidently HTML and JSON artifacts for data quality\n",
+        "- `monitoring_summary.json` with the exact S3 files used\n"
+      ]
+    },
+    {
+      "cell_type": "markdown",
+      "metadata": {},
+      "source": [
+        "## Section 8: Schedule the Pipeline with EventBridge Scheduler\n",
+        "\n",
